                </div>
                <h5 class="fw-800 text-white mb-3 fs-4" style="line-height: 1.4;">Start-up to Unicorn Accolade in Solar Innovation</h5>
                <p class="card-body-text small mb-0">Honored by Cabinet Minister Sh. Piyush Goyal Ji, celebrating our groundbreaking work and rapid growth from a promising startup to a leading force in the sector.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start mb-4">
