                <p class="card-body-text small mb-0">Presented by CM Sh. Pushkar Singh Dhami Ji, acknowledging EAPRO’s role in driving solar innovation and generating meaningful employment in Uttarakhand.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-5 p-4 rounded-4 text-center" style="background: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.2);">
